First Lady Thobeka Madiba-Zuma has given South Africans a glimpse into how the Zuma family celebrates Father s Day with the country s first citizen, President Jacob Zuma. On Sunday Madiba-Zuma posted a video on her Instagram account showing some of Zuma s children huddled around him to sing to their dad a special happy father s day to you song while he cut a cake to celebrate with them. The only thing better than having you as my hubby, is my children having you as a Dad, the first lady said in her post. Watch the video below: The only thing better than having you as my hubby, is my children having you as a Dad. #fathersday #mom #diaryofagratefulmom #numberonedad A post shared by TMZF Founder &amp; Patron (@firstladytzuma) on Jun 18, 2017 at 4:15am PDT Happy Father s Day to all the dads out there! ALSO READ: Robert Marawa faces being fired from Metro FM